        <item>
            <title>1.5.4</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 12:46:21 -0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>14</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.5.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>1.5.4</h2>
<p>You can now mark a bill paid weeks ahead — Otto asks once to make sure, then records it. Also fixes the app feeling frozen while Otto is typing, and restores the August SMUD payment that yesterday's update wrongly removed.</p>
]]></description>
